<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 251, 244); text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">高能预警！</span><span style="text-indent: 0em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;">新学期来临！</span></span><span style="text-indent: 0em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">考试周即将到达战场！</span><span style="text-indent: 0em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">不知经管的同学们复习的怎么样了？</span><span style="text-indent: 0em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">是坚信复习随缘，有缘自能记起<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red;">？</span></span><span style="text-indent: 0em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">还是正在图书馆里奋笔疾书，一目十行？</span><span style="text-indent: 0em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);">或是已经准备万全自信应考了？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 251, 244); overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="text-indent: 0em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEITwiazuFM74ic7coRUPhhX3EcAwPXQfXMBMibzmGUIbhPEzPBKfcqUu9wxaAf1nMPOoQGzSSSAuCcQA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="195" height="183" style="width: 195px; height: 183px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 251, 244); text-align: center; color: rgb(123, 173, 214); font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">但不论复习得如何,</span><span style="text-indent: 0em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">对接下来要开始的考试周,</span><span style="text-indent: 0em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我们需做到</span><span style="text-indent: 0em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">诚信考试，拒绝舞弊！</span><strong style="text-indent: 0em; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">考试千万条，诚信第一条！</span></strong></p><p><br/></p>